{"tid":2463111,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"25歲報稱公務員女子懷疑挪用眾籌資金　涉洗黑錢被捕","createTime":"2021-03-26T12:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T13:47:00.000Z","uid":13395,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"975963b78e525e4298f4790b0c537aeb00ef0fe0","tid":2463111,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12:40:24.000Z","msg":"25歲報稱公務員女子懷疑挪用眾籌資金　涉洗黑錢被捕<br />\n<br />\n警方以「洗黑錢」罪拘捕一名25歲報稱是公務員的本地女子，目前正被扣查。警方說，早前接獲線報，懷疑有人透過社交平台，聲稱為支持被捕人士的生活而發起眾籌，向公眾提供兩個公司銀行戶口資料作收款用途，但其後挪用眾籌資金用以個人消費，包括購買名牌手袋、電子產品及證劵買賣等，與眾籌目的不同，涉嫌干犯欺詐罪，而處理有關款項就可能構成「洗黑錢」罪。警方又說，在2019年8月至2020年12月期間，該兩個公司銀行戶口，共收取約208萬港元，部分款項轉帳到另一個本地個人銀行戶口，有關個人戶口另外亦收取了約250萬來歷不明的資金。被捕的女子為涉案個人戶口的其中一名認可簽署人。警方在行動中檢取了現金、電話、銀行文件等，並凍結了相關銀行及證券戶口約27萬元，目前正追查資金的來源及去向，而案中亦有兩名主腦，分別是一名20歲男子，為涉案公司董事及戶口持有人，另一名29歲男子則為個人戶口持有人，兩人已於去年8月離開香港，目前正被警方通緝。<br />\n<br />\n2021-03-26 20:33:16<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582814-20210326.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582814-20210326.htm&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWkPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=71141d8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582814-20210326.htm&h=fe01838d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582814-20210326.htm</a>"},{"pid":"df5c297cf9f99ebc0d01d7f67c4fd971497a0e3f","tid":2463111,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:25:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d75e78219bf4a0b620af0780bde84e2d6fec148","tid":2463111,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f0e03c3f948e616c439673c355d74b2e4ab37b4","tid":2463111,"uid":274772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:38:52.000Z","msg":"黑警口中嘅嘢 100%唔信"},{"pid":"2433e9472c8437d971fdec407f7301d25379a5dd","tid":2463111,"uid":26014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:47:00.000Z","msg":"支持佢生活唔可以支持佢奢侈咁生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}